text: Shawn Hernandez (born February 11, 1973 in Houston, Texas) is an American professional wrestler. He is best known by the ring name, Hernandez. He is currently signed to Total Nonstop Action Wrestling. Hernandez is also known for forming the tag team stable, The Latin American Xchange with Homicide which ended when he was betrayed by Homicide and was attacked by him on the September 10 edition of TNA Impact!. He has been a two time NWA World Tag Team Champion with Homicide and a two time TNA World Tag Team Champion with Homicide (once) and Matt Morgan (once). He also won the Deuces Wild Tournament in 2008 with Homicide. His finishing move is called the Border Toss which is a throwing crucifix powerbomb. ==References== == Other websites == *Shawn Hernandez's Official website *Shawn Hernandez's TNA profile Category:1973 births Category:American professional wrestlers Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Houston
